PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782847100
OL,3,CWife of Rag'n'Bone Man spared jail
OL,4,Cafter crash involving family-of-four
OL,6,FLewes Crown Court heard Samantha was
OL,7,Fturning right, crossing the
OL,8,Fcarriageway in front of Graham, when
OL,9,Fshe smashed into her at at least 50mph.
OL,11,FDespite overtaking a line of cars, the
OL,12,Fcourt heard Graham was not breaking
OL,13,Fthe speed limit.
OL,15,FGraham apologised and said she had
OL,16,Fbeen late to pick up her own children
OL,17,Ffrom school at the time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
