PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782847100
OL,3,CWife of Rag'n'Bone Man spared jail
OL,4,Cafter crash involving family-of-four
OL,6,FSamantha is said to have pleaded with
OL,7,Fparamedics not to leave her children
OL,8,Forphaned after losing her husband in
OL,9,Fanother car accident a year before.
OL,11,FHis Honour Judge David Rennie told
OL,12,FGraham: "The pre-sentence report has
OL,13,Fgiven me a wealth of information about
OL,14,Fyou, your family and your background.
OL,16,F"I've read references from people who
OL,17,Fknow you very well and they speak very
OL,18,Fhighly of you.
OL,20,F"I've read and considered the report
OL,21,Ffrom the consultant psychiatrist.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782847100
OL,3,CWife of Rag'n'Bone Man spared jail
OL,4,Cafter crash involving family-of-four
OL,6,F"I regard what you did on this
OL,7,Foccasion as wholly out of character.
OL,9,F"I have no doubt you are deeply,
OL,10,Fdeeply sorry for what you did to - as
OL,11,Fyou say - another mum."
OL,13,FThe crash had a profound and ongoing
OL,14,Fimpact on Mrs Keen and her family, the
OL,15,Fjudge said.
OL,17,F"Life is pretty grim for her and I
OL,18,Fknow you get it," the judge said.
OL,20,F"If you had driven in the way you were
OL,21,Fsupposed to.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782847100
OL,3,CWife of Rag'n'Bone Man spared jail
OL,4,Cafter crash involving family-of-four
OL,6,F"This is one of those horrendous cases
OL,7,Fwhere two families have been left
OL,8,Fdevastated by the nature of the
OL,9,Fdriving.
OL,11,F"I'm confident you will never, ever
OL,12,Fbehave in a way which will bring you
OL,13,Fback to court."
OL,15,FThe court heard Graham was originally
OL,16,Fcharged with causing serious injury by
OL,17,Fdangerous driving. The Crown accepted
OL,18,Fher guilty plea to the lesser charge
OL,19,Fof causing serious injury by careless
OL,20,Fdriving.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
